bumblebee (3.0-1~preciseppa3) precise; urgency=low

  * patches/001-no-set-ldpath.patch:
    - Allow nouveau to function properly even with nvidia installed.
  * patches/002-ignore-empty-kerneldriver.patch:
    - Properly treat an empty KernelDriver setting as "use the Driver setting".
  * patches/003-no-crash-on-invalid-pm-method.patch:
    - Do not crash on invalid PmMethod or --pm-method.
  * patches/004-remove-switcheroo-restriction.patch:
    - Allow vgaswitcheroo to be used for drivers other than nouveau. This may be
      useful for gmux and others.
  * Restore OpenGL alternatives configuration on uninstallation.
  * Recommend 32-bit virtualgl libraries.

 -- Peter Lekensteyn <lekensteyn@gmail.com>  Fri, 27 Apr 2012 00:30:06 +0200

bumblebee (3.0-1~oneiricppa2) oneiric; urgency=low

  * Trigger update of initial ramdisk to get conflicting drivers blacklisted.
  * debian/control:
    - Fix lintian warnings: debhelper version
  * Include debugging symbols in bumblebee-dbg.

